================================================================================
                       VIOLATION REPORTING PROCEDURE
================================================================================

If you believe this software is being used in violation of the AGPLv3:

1. DOCUMENT the violation (screenshots, URLs, specific instances)
2. COLLECT evidence of non-compliance
3. CONTACT us via email with detailed information
4. ALLOW reasonable time for investigation and resolution

Common violations include:
- Distribution without source code
- Removal of copyright notices
- Network services not offering source code
- Relicensing under different terms

We take license compliance seriously and will address legitimate violations
promptly and professionally.

